	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				<a href="http://www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-platon">Responsive Joomla template for Universities and colleges - JA Platon</a>
				<h4><a href="http://www.joomlart.com/joomla/templates/ja-platon" title="">Home</a> | <a href="http://joomlart.com/demo/#ja_platon" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="http://www.joomlart.com/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-platon" title="">Document</a> | <a href="http://pm.joomlart.com/browse/JATCPLATON" title="">Changelog</a></h4>
				<p>Welcome JA Platon (December Template) - Responsive Joomla Template for Universities and Colleges. </p>
				<p>It is a perfect new Joomla 3 template for Universities, schools, colleges and other educational websites. JA Platon supports Kunena - Joomla forum component and Jomsocial 4 - Joomla social networking extensions. With Kunena, and JomSocial 4, Platon creates not only a school websites, but also discussion boards, forums and social platforms for educational organizations. </p>
				<p>Thanks to T3 Framework and Bootstrap 3, JA Platon is a fully responsive Joomla 3 template. Platon has intuitive Admin panel with easy to use options and built-in tools. The template is easy to customize as users' needs. The site speed is also optimized for better performance and user experience. </p>
				<p>JA Platon supports RTL languages layout.</p>
				<span style="color:#FF0000">Note: JA Platon template requires T3 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span><p></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2016 <a href='http://www.joomlart.com/' title='Visit Joomlart.com!'>JoomlArt.com</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
